[[Sergeant/Legends|Sergeant]] '''Baras Perosei''' was a [[Gender/Legends|male]] [[Human/Legends|Human]] from the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Naboo/Legends|Naboo]] who served as a [[Naboo Palace Guard/Legends|Palace Guard]] of the [[Royal Naboo Security Forces/Legends|Royal Naboo Security Forces]].

==Biography==
[[File:Perosei.jpg|thumb|left|180px|Sergeant Perosei in the [[Theed Royal Palace/Legends|Theed Royal Palace]]]]
During the [[Trade Federation/Legends|Trade Federation's]] [[Invasion of Naboo/Legends|occupation of Naboo]], Perosei was held prisoner at [[Camp Four/Legends|Camp Four]]<ref name="CCG">{{CCG|set=Theed Palace Limited|cardname=Officer Perosei}}</ref> until he was [[Liberation of Camp Four|rescued]] by the [[Naboo Resistance]], led by [[Lieutenant/Legends|Lieutenant]] [[Gavyn Sykes/Legends|Gavyn Sykes]].<ref name="BFN">''[[Star Wars: Episode I: Battle for Naboo]]''</ref> During the [[Battle of Naboo/Legends|Battle of Naboo]], he helped [[Queen/Legends|Queen]] [[Padmé Amidala/Legends|Padmé Amidala]] capture the [[Neimoidian/Legends|Neimoidian]] [[Viceroy/Legends|Viceroy]] [[Nute Gunray/Legends|Nute Gunray]].<ref name="Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace">{{Film|I}}</ref>

Perosei was known to be able to assemble and disassemble a [[S-5 heavy blaster pistol/Legends|S-5 heavy blaster pistol]] in less than sixty [[Standard second|seconds]].<ref name="CCG" />

